org.dellroad.jibxbindings.vcard

Class VCardMarshaller

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jibx.extras.DocumentModelMapperBase
      • org.jibx.extras.DomMapperBase
        • org.jibx.extras.DomElementMapper
          • org.dellroad.jibxbindings.vcard.VCardMarshaller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAliasable, IMarshaller, IUnmarshaller

    public class VCardMarshaller
extends DomElementMapper
    JiBX marshaller/unmarshaller for a single VCard.

    Example of use: 

      <mapping ... >
      <namespace uri="urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:vcard-4.0" prefix="vc"/>
      ...
      <structure name="ContactInfo">
          <structure name="vcard" field="contactInfo" ns="urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:vcard-4.0"
            marshaller="org.dellroad.jibxbindings.vcard.VCardMarshaller"
            unmarshaller="org.dellroad.jibxbindings.vcard.VCardMarshaller"/>
      </structure>
      ...
  </mapping>

    See Also:
    The EZ-vCard Project, RFC 6351
